document_data.Defenses:
Thentia had one of the weakest militaries among the Moonsea powers. They were guarded by a cavalry of some sixty mounted soldiers known as the [[Riders of Thentia]].{{Cite polyhedron/79/The Everwinking Eye: Inside Thentia|7-8}}

The city watch known as the Warders served as Thentia's police force. 10 of whom were always stationed at the [[Watchlord's Tower]].

While Thentia boasted no navy, their ships were protected by city's resident spellcasters. In truth, Thentia's [[archmage]]s were impressive enough in their own right to discourage open aggression taken towards the city or their sea trade.
